From df86bd2491bf2f88df2e84074140d5f261bdd5b6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: KARTHIK KUMAR T <kartt@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 14 Aug 2025 23:56:36 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:DP:wifi:ath12k: Optimizations for KPI performance

- Reorganized `pdev_idx` in `ath12k` struct for better cache alignment.
- Reordered DP stats knobs in `ath12k_pdev_dp` to improve cache efficiency.
- Adjusted `tx_fast_unicast` placement in `ath12k_device_dp_stats`
  for cache alignment.
- Increased TX ring size to 2048 for enhanced throughput.
- Added `unlikely()` conditions in fast path to optimize branch prediction.
- Forked out a new function for fast path packet enqueue to improve
  i-cache and d-cache alignment.

Patch-dependency: None

Signed-off-by: KARTHIK KUMAR T <kartt@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Sai Rupesh Chevuru <chevuru@qti.qualcomm.com>
